{"tid":1030982,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"3場賽事定沙里生死！！！","createTime":"2019-02-21T10:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T11:06:11.000Z","uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"93a4a4b499cbf6d8c3fd07d0e403d93dd693b04f","tid":1030982,"uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:49:56.000Z","msg":"車路士領隊沙里在球隊的時間進入倒數階段，<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=a81f362a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>收到消息，未來3場成績將決定沙里的生死。<br />\n<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=a81f362a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>收到消息，若果車路士未來三戰，分別歐聯次回合對馬模、聯賽盃對曼城及聯賽對熱刺成績不理想的話，球隊會解僱沙里，然後請臨時領隊接手。<br />\n<br />\n車路士雖然在聯賽盃殺入決賽，但足總盃被曼聯淘汰，聯賽亦跌出前四。有傳車路士已有後備領隊名單，雖然未有公開，但助教蘇拿及紐頓其中一人有機接手。其中紐頓在干地離隊後，沙里接手前已帶過一隊操練。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.egypttoday.com/images/larg/37240.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.egypttoday.com%2Fimages%2Flarg%2F37240.jpg&h=3db916d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a81e2fda2c1c052f8c194d228a86055af3c27207","tid":1030982,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:00:36.000Z","msg":"希汀克就希汀克啦，臨時領隊賣晒關子咁"},{"pid":"ce51a6d84a38a7841c4f9fd636748a3bb474bafc","tid":1030982,"uid":25831,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:06:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}